Northwest
won't put the
SQUEEZE
on you.
Most airlines are squeezing an extra seat into every
Coach and Economy row on their wide-cabin jets. But
not Northwest. We give you wider seats, wider
armrests, more comfort all around. A good reason to
fly across the U.S.A., Canada, the Orient and Europe
on the roomy wide-cabin airline — Northwest!
